with the naked eye.

00:15:53.010 --> 00:15:56.340 align:middle line:84%
To this day, the
enigma of the origin

00:15:56.340 --> 00:15:59.140 align:middle line:84%
of the body image of
the Shroud of Turin

00:15:59.140 --> 00:16:01.910 align:middle line:84%
is a challenge to
our intelligence

00:16:01.910 --> 00:16:05.440 align:middle line:90%
and to our science.

00:16:05.440 --> 00:16:09.120 align:middle line:84%
Experts are in agreement that
the image on the linen shroud

00:16:09.120 --> 00:16:13.730 align:middle line:84%
