substance such as paint

00:16:13.730 --> 00:16:15.360 align:middle line:90%
or pigment.

00:16:15.360 --> 00:16:18.510 align:middle line:84%
This means it's
not a photograph.

00:16:18.510 --> 00:16:22.400 align:middle line:84%
