alteration of the surface

00:16:22.400 --> 00:16:27.930 align:middle line:84%
of the linen by some effect
of light or radiation,

00:16:27.930 --> 00:16:33.450 align:middle line:84%
something which also
makes linen turn yellow.

00:16:33.450 --> 00:16:38.300 align:middle line:84%
