00:23:48.810 --> 00:23:50.890 align:middle line:90%
the resurrected Christ.

00:23:50.890 --> 00:23:54.840 align:middle line:84%
If one views the Shroud
of Turin as an icon,

00:23:54.840 --> 00:23:58.300 align:middle line:84%
