hologram on the cloth.

00:25:43.960 --> 00:25:46.490 align:middle line:84%
She says the entire
resurrection process

00:25:46.490 --> 00:25:50.500 align:middle line:84%
is akin to the Big Bang creation
of the universe, when something

00:25:50.500 --> 00:25:52.440 align:middle line:90%
was created from nothing.

00:25:52.440 --> 00:25:54.330 align:middle line:84%
You can read the
science of the shroud,

00:25:54.330 --> 00:25:57.420 align:middle line:84%
such as the total lack of
gravity, lack of entropy

00:25:57.420 --> 00:26:01.150 align:middle line:84%
without gravitational collapse,
no time, no space-- it conforms

00:26:01.150 --> 00:26:04.750 align:middle line:90%
to no known law of physics.

00:26:04.750 --> 00:26:08.780 align:middle line:84%
And according to the nature of
the event horizon, says Piczek,

00:26:08.780 --> 00:26:11.720 align:middle line:84%
the dead body must
have left its image

00:26:11.720 --> 00:26:14.600 align:middle line:84%
on the two surfaces
of the event horizons.

